headline: T. Rowe Price (TROW) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of investment management firm T. Rowe Price (NASDAQ:TROW) fell 3.1% in the afternoon session after the company reported preliminary month-end assets under management for November that showed significant net outflows. T. Rowe Price announced that its assets under management (AUM) were $1.79 trillion at the end of November.
